author: COMSOL
description: This model reproduces a NAFEMS benchmark in which a plate with an angle crack is subjected to tensile loading. The J-integral is calculated and the stress intensity factors for Mode I and Mode II are compared to the benchmark for several values of the angle.
label: angle_crack_plate.mph
